window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>\"I can command storms, summon fire and unmake stone,\" Balfruss growled. \"It's dangerous to meddle with things you don't understand.\"</i> </p> <p><b>Balfruss</b> is a battlemage, sworn to fight and die for a country that fears and despises his kind. </p> <p><b>Vargus</b> is a common soldier - while mages shoot lightning from the walls of the city, he's down in the front lines getting blood on his blade. </p> <p><b>Talandra</b> is a princess and spymaster, but the war may force her to risk everything and make the greatest sacrifice of all. </p> <p><b>Magic and mayhem collide in this explosive epic fantasy from a major new talent. </b> </p>"; 
